@startuml

actor Editora

participant ArticleDashboard
participant ReviewerAssignmentPanel
participant ReviewerManager
participant ReviewerStorage
participant ArticleManager
participant ArticleStorage

Editora -> ArticleDashboard : Selecciona artículo
ArticleDashboard -> ReviewerAssignmentPanel : Abrir panel asignación

Editora -> ReviewerAssignmentPanel : Seleccionar revisores
ReviewerAssignmentPanel -> ReviewerManager : assignReviewers(article, reviewers)

ReviewerManager -> ReviewerStorage : saveAssignment(data)
ReviewerStorage --> ReviewerManager : confirmación

ReviewerAssignmentPanel -> ArticleManager : updateStatus("En revisión")
ArticleManager -> ArticleStorage : update(article)
ArticleStorage --> ArticleManager : confirmación

ArticleManager --> ReviewerAssignmentPanel : éxito
ReviewerAssignmentPanel --> Editora : Mostrar confirmación

@enduml
